hopobject.body: What sort of music do you listen to? cual es el precio de xenical en costa rica When Alex Mack starts to come to terms with her new powers, she's got to confide in someone. Darris Love plays Ray Alvarado, her neighbor, best friend and practically brother, who helps Alex cope with life post-chemical spill. Darris Love's role on 'Alex Mack' was only the second time he'd hit the big screen. After the show, he scored the part of Jamal on 'Sister, Sister.' He's also been a one-off actor in other series like 'Buffy the Vampire Slayer' and 'ER.' Love is also known for his role as Alonzo in 'Gang Tapes' (2001).
